### 2. Betriebsausgaben – business expenses (§ 4 Abs 4 EStG)

**Applies to:** self-employed, freelancers, trades, farmers.

**Examples:** office rent, goods purchased for resale, vehicle operating costs, professional insurance, advertising.

**Deductible share:** 100 % if the expense is incurred “to earn, secure or maintain” business income. Mixed-use items must be apportioned (e.g. 60 % business / 40 % private).

