### 4. Außergewöhnliche Belastungen – extraordinary burdens (§ 33 – § 33b EStG)

#### 4a. General (§ 33)

*Unreimbursed medical bills, dentures, funeral costs, storm damage, etc.*

**Deductible only above a sliding “zumutbare Belastung” threshold** (≈ 1 %–7 % of income depending on family status).

#### 4b. Specific lump sums

| Lump sum                                     | 2025 amount / conditions                                                                |
|---------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| Behinderten-Pauschbetrag                    | € 384 (GdB 20) ⇢ € 2 840 (GdB 100); € 7 400 for blind / “hilflos” persons               |
| Pflege-Pauschbetrag for carers              | € 600 (PG 2), € 1 100 (PG 3), € 1 800 (PG 4/5 or hilflos)                               |
| Unterhalt an bedürftige Personen (§ 33a I)  | Bis zu Höhe des Grundfreibetrags (2025 = € 12 096) pro Jahr                             |

**Effect:** Either a lump-sum deduction or actual costs minus threshold.

