### 5. Direkte Steuerermäßigungen – tax credits (§ 35a, § 35c EStG)

| Credit                                       | What is promoted                                                             | Share & cap                                                             |
|---------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| Minijob im Haushalt (§ 35a I)               | Babysitter, cleaner employed via Minijob-Zentrale                            | 20 % of wages, max € 510 credit p.a.                                   |
| Haushaltsnahe Dienstleistungen (§ 35a II 1) | Regular cleaning service, gardening, care services                           | 20 % of costs, max € 4 000 credit p.a.                                  |
| Handwerkerleistungen (§ 35a III)            | Renovation, repairs inside the home                                          | 20 % of labour costs, max € 1 200 credit p.a.                           |
| Energetic renovation (§ 35c)                | Insulation, new windows, heating upgrade on own home ≥ 10 yrs old            | 20 % of eligible costs spread over 3 yrs, max € 40 000 per property     |

**Effect:** These amounts are subtracted after the tax is calculated – more powerful than a normal deduction.

